Authors of CMEM 
==================

The main development of the Community Microwave Emission Modelling Platform is done through the 

            Data Assimilation Section 

at the

       European Centre for Medium-Range Weather Forecasts 
               (ECMWF - http://www.ecmwf.int ). 

and

       Institut National the Recheches Agronomiques (France)
                      (INRA  -  http://www.inra.fr/)


Main programmers:
=================

Patricia de Rosnay
Joaquin Munoz Sabater

Past contributors:
==================

Matthias Drusch (ECMWF)
Thomas Holmes  (INPE)
Jean-Pierre Wigneron (INRA)

SATOPE_CLM4CMEM:
This is a derivations from original CMEM, to calculate Satellite TBs
usin CLM as input. For the DFG project FOR2131
====================================================================

Pablo Saavedra G. (UNI BONN) [pablosaa@uni-bonn.de]

